🎉 COVER REVEAL GIVE-AWAY! 🎉
 
We are so excited to join in the official book cover makeover reveal for @kristincanaryauthor’s California Dreamin’ series. These closed-door romcoms are the perfect dose of sunshine…and now their covers reflect that!
 
And what’s a cover reveal without a give-away???
 
We’ll be giving away A COMPLETE SET of the newly covered California Dreamin’ books (paperback for U.S. addresses, ebook for international). Woohoo! Who’s ready to play?
 
Entering is super easy! Just do the following:
 
💙Follow each of our accounts:
@kristincanaryauthor
@delightfullybooked
@thebookscript
@aprilsbooknook_
@bookswithnopictures
@sweet.cleanreads
@marilee.loves.to.read
@chelseas.book.channel

💙Tag at least 2 bookish friends.
 
💙Tell us which new cover you love the most!
 
💙Share in your stories for an extra entry.
 
That’s it! Give-away entries end on Friday at 11:59pm Pacific.
 
By the way, there are FOUR chances to enter as we’ve got four videos posted here on the ‘gram. 🙌 We will each randomly select a finalist from our posts and then the WINNER will be randomly selected from those four finalists. So be sure to interact with each video! Let’s get this party started!
 
👉Here’s a note from Kristin: I love these stories and am honored to give them fresh life with these beautiful covers. And thanks so much to these awesome ladies for helping me celebrate! Good luck with the giveaway, everyone.
 
Giveaway is not sponsored or endorsed by Instagram in any way.

